<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Privacy Policy | Workmedix', description: 'Workmedix Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information in compliance with POPIA.', canonicalPath: '/privacy' }) %>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<main style="padding-top:120px;padding-bottom:80px;min-height:80vh;">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px;">

    <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--mid-grey);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Last updated: May 2025 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Effective immediately</p>

    <div class="privacy-body">

      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Workmedix ("we", "our", "us") is a South African occupational health screening service provider. We are the Responsible Party for your personal information as defined under the Protection of Personal Information Act 4 of 2013 (<strong>POPIA</strong>).</p>
      <p><strong>Contact:</strong> info@workmedix.co.za &nbsp;|&nbsp; 074 716 3079 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Johannesburg, Gauteng, South Africa</p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect only the personal information necessary to provide our services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account data:</strong> name, email address, company name, password (hashed — never stored in plain text)</li>
        <li><strong>Contact enquiries:</strong> name, company, email, phone number, service interest, message content</li>
        <li><strong>Screening records:</strong> health screening results, medical certificates, and related occupational health documents uploaded by authorised users</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> standard server logs (IP address, browser type, pages visited) for security and performance monitoring</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Your information is used exclusively to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide and manage occupational health screening services</li>
        <li>Respond to your enquiries and communicate with you</li>
        <li>Maintain and secure your client portal account</li>
        <li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations (including the Occupational Health and Safety Act)</li>
        <li>Improve the performance and security of our platform</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or trade your personal information to any third party.</p>

      <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
      <p>We process your personal information on the following lawful grounds under POPIA:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contract:</strong> to fulfil our service agreement with you</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> to maintain platform security and communicate relevant service updates</li>
        <li><strong>Consent:</strong> for optional communications (you may withdraw consent at any time)</li>
        <li><strong>Legal obligation:</strong> where required by South African law</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
      <p>Your data is stored on secure cloud infrastructure (Railway, hosted in managed data centres). We implement industry-standard safeguards including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>HTTPS/TLS encryption for all data in transit</li>
        <li>Bcrypt password hashing (cost factor 12)</li>
        <li>HTTP-only, secure, SameSite session cookies</li>
        <li>Strict security headers (CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options)</li>
        <li>Rate limiting on authentication and contact endpoints</li>
        <li>Role-based access control (admin vs. client)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain personal information only for as long as necessary:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Account data: for the duration of your account plus 3 years after closure</li>
        <li>Screening records: as required by applicable occupational health regulations (typically 5–40 years depending on record type)</li>
        <li>Contact enquiries: 2 years</li>
        <li>Server logs: 90 days</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>7. Your Rights Under POPIA</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to your personal information</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your information (subject to legal retention obligations)</li>
        <li>Object to processing of your information</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with the <strong>Information Regulator of South Africa</strong> at <a href="https://inforegulator.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener">inforegulator.org.za</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any right, email us at <a href="mailto:info@workmedix.co.za">info@workmedix.co.za</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>

      <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use only one cookie: a session cookie (<code>wm.sid</code>) to maintain your logged-in state. It is HTTP-only, secure, and expires after 24 hours. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or third-party analytics.</p>

      <h2>9. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following trusted services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Railway:</strong> cloud hosting infrastructure</li>
        <li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> typography (loaded client-side)</li>
        <li><strong>Resend / SMTP:</strong> transactional email delivery only</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our services are directed at corporate clients and are not intended for individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect information from minors.</p>

      <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the platform after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

      <h2>12. Contact &amp; Complaints</h2>
      <p>For any privacy-related query or to exercise your rights:</p>
      <p>
        <strong>Workmedix</strong><br>
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@workmedix.co.za">info@workmedix.co.za</a><br>
        Phone: 074 716 3079<br>
        Johannesburg, Gauteng, South Africa
      </p>

    </div>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<style>
.privacy-body h2 {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--primary-dark);
  margin: 2.2rem 0 .75rem;
}
.privacy-body p, .privacy-body li {
  color: var(--mid-grey);
  font-size: .95rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: .6rem;
}
.privacy-body ul {
  padding-left: 1.4rem;
  list-style: disc;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.privacy-body a { color: var(--accent); }
.privacy-body code {
  background: var(--off-white);
  padding: .1rem .4rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: .85rem;
}
</style>
</body>
</html>
